item.title: git
item.description: 上传至仓库 git init git remote add origin https://github.com/chenxuefan/chenxuefan.github.io.git git add . git commit -m"update" git branch git push -u origin master 配置git环境 sudo yum install git git config –global user.name chenxuefan git config –global user.email 2380540710@qq.com ssh-keygen -t rsa -C “2380540710@qq.com” cat /home/chenxuefan/.ssh/id_rsa.pub ssh -T git@github.com sudo git clone https://github.com/chenxuefan/dytt.git
